#

Simple Apple Cranberry Sauce

25 min
$3.5
100 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 8

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVegan

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side DishCondiment

Tags:

SauceSidesHoliday

Description

A sweet and tart sauce perfect for holiday meals or as a delicious topping for breakfast.

Ingredients

  • fresh cranberries: 2 cups
  • apple (peeled, cored, and chopped): 1 large
  • sugar: 1 cup
  • water: 1 cup
  • cinnamon (optional): 1/2 teaspoon
